Designed for traders who want to capture strong market trends using a simple and clear EMA-based trading system.
A simple and effective trend-following strategy using EMA crossovers and ATR-based risk management to capture strong crypto market trends.

📘 How to Use

1️⃣ Add the strategy to your chart on TradingView.

2️⃣ Use it on BTC or other crypto assets.

3️⃣ Recommended timeframes:

1H

4H

1D

4️⃣ The strategy automatically generates:

LONG signals when bullish momentum appears

SHORT signals when bearish momentum appears

5️⃣ Each trade displays:

Entry price

Stop Loss

Take Profit levels (TP1 and TP2)

6️⃣ Use the built-in dashboard to analyze:

Net Profit

Winrate

Total Trades

Max Drawdown

7️⃣ For best results, use the strategy in trending markets and avoid trading during strong consolidation.
